        <review>&lt;span class="Apple-style-span" style="line-height: 20px; font-family: sans-serif; "/&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 0.4em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; "&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;Dream of the Red Chamber&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#160;(&lt;a shape="rect" class="" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Simplified_Chinese_characters" title="Simplified Chinese characters" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "&gt;simplified Chinese&lt;/a&gt;:&#160;&lt;span lang="zh-Hans"&gt;红楼梦&lt;/span&gt;;&#160;&lt;a shape="rect" class="" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Traditional_Chinese_characters" title="Traditional Chinese characters" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "&gt;traditional Chinese&lt;/a&gt;:&#160;&lt;span lang="zh-Hant"&gt;紅樓夢&lt;/span&gt;;&#160;&lt;a shape="rect" class="" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pinyin" title="Pinyin" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "&gt;pinyin&lt;/a&gt;:&#160;&lt;em&gt;Hóng Lóu Mèng&lt;/em&gt;;&#160;&lt;a shape="rect" class="" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wade%E2%80%93Giles" title="Wade–Giles" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "&gt;Wade–Giles&lt;/a&gt;: Hung Lou Meng), composed by&#160;&lt;a shape="rect" class="" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cao_Xueqin" title="Cao Xueqin" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "&gt;Cao Xueqin&lt;/a&gt;, is one of China's&lt;a shape="rect" class="" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Four_Great_Classical_Novels" title="Four Great Classical Novels" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "&gt;Four Great Classical Novels&lt;/a&gt;. It was composed sometime in the middle of the 18th century during the&#160;&lt;a shape="rect" class="" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Qing_Dynasty" title="Qing Dynasty" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "&gt;Qing Dynasty&lt;/a&gt;. It is a masterpiece of&#160;&lt;a shape="rect" class="" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chinese_literature" title="Chinese literature" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "&gt;Chinese vernacular literature&lt;/a&gt;&#160;and is generally acknowledged to be the pinnacle of classical Chinese novels. "&lt;a shape="rect" class="" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Redology" title="Redology" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "&gt;Redology&lt;/a&gt;" is the field of study devoted exclusively to this work.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 0.4em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; "&gt;The novel's name may alternatively be translated as&#160;&lt;i&gt;Red Chamber Dream&lt;/i&gt;&#160;or&#160;&lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;A Dream of Red Mansions&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;, and it is sometimes referred to by another name,&#160;&lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;The Story of the Stone&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;(&lt;a shape="rect" class="" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Simplified_Chinese_characters" title="Simplified Chinese characters" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "&gt;simplified Chinese&lt;/a&gt;:&#160;&lt;span lang="zh-Hans"&gt;石头记&lt;/span&gt;;&#160;&lt;a shape="rect" class="" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Traditional_Chinese_characters" title="Traditional Chinese characters" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "&gt;traditional Chinese&lt;/a&gt;:&#160;&lt;span lang="zh-Hant"&gt;石頭記&lt;/span&gt;;&#160;&lt;a shape="rect" class="" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pinyin" title="Pinyin" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "&gt;pinyin&lt;/a&gt;:&#160;&lt;em&gt;Shítóu jì&lt;/em&gt;; literally "Record of the Stone"). Only the first 80 chapters were written by Cao Xueqin. Various authors have submitted more than 100 alternate endings, often adding 40 additional chapters to complete the novel.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 0.4em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; "&gt;&lt;i&gt;Red Chamber&lt;/i&gt;&#160;is believed to be semi-&lt;a shape="rect" class="mw-redirect" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Autobiographical" title="Autobiographical" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "&gt;autobiographical&lt;/a&gt;, mirroring the fortunes of author Cao Xueqin's own family. As the author details in the first chapter, it is intended to be a memorial to the women he knew in his youth: friends, relatives and servants. The novel is remarkable not only for its huge cast of characters and psychological scope, but also for its precise and detailed observation of the life and social structures typical of 18th-century Chinese aristocracy.&lt;br clear="none"/&gt;&lt;br clear="none"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 11px; line-height: 15px; "&gt;Text is available under the&#160;&lt;a shape="rect" rel="license" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Text_of_Creative_Commons_Attribution-ShareAlike_3.0_Unported_License" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "&gt;Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike License&lt;/a&gt;; additional terms may apply. See&#160;&lt;a shape="rect" href="http://wikimediafoundation.org/wiki/Terms_of_Use" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(6, 69, 173); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "&gt;Terms of Use&lt;/a&gt;&#160;for details.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br clear="none"/&gt;</review>
